{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"11949-the-kite","title":"The Kite","description":"Open the book. Spot the kite. See what happens to it. Enjoy the crisp lines and the Warli art.","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Jeyanthi Manokaran"],"illustrators":["Jeyanthi Manokaran"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Books","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/11949-the-kite"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/117638/size3/ac6a77ff9d0dd2a0a61098ad0557ff0c.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/117638/size6/ac6a77ff9d0dd2a0a61098ad0557ff0c.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/33712/size6/44f1bbc4c8f7c4bdc3497f956efb8f25.jpg","text":"Look! A kite fight!\nOops! The purple kite\nis torn.\nOh no! The yellow one’s\ngone.\nAha! The red kite\nfloats down.\nClimb up high.\nStretch out and grab!","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/33713/size6/743edc4a30edf345d970adee29e85839.jpg","text":"Quick! Zoom away.\nNow step inside\nand hide.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/33714/size6/9df3bb3bffafe0b12f9f10d521f791f5.jpg","text":"Sprint right\nthrough without a stop.\nSlide over and\ndodge about.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/33715/size6/73ddad45c74d370e3fedf4d9f8ee569d.jpg","text":"Ride on, don’t let\nthem load the hay.\nHop off! Zig-zag through the market.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/33716/size6/effedb7cc52780fc8da91de7e2a91c59.jpg","text":"Charge along, try\nnot to crash.\nPush through\nfaster! Make a dash!","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/33717/size6/5aefa5f8c26904fac0601451261c0198.jpg","text":"Yay! Hurray! It's all mine!\nThis red kite now\nbelongs to me.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/33718/size6/75cc01b368448df630e9146bf5805f41.jpg","text":"Oh no!\nAnother chase?","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":7,"words":90}}